Job Description
To work with sales and the team to ensure smooth handover of confirmed exhibitors and manage the logistic, overall exhibition planning and execution;
To develop and monitor overall working schedule, exhibition planning, logistic arrangement;
To take care and coordinate with exhibitors, ensure smooth handover from sales team;
To provide consultation and superior project management services for exhibitors;
To handle enquiries from exhibitors/ visitors and undertake on-site duties during exhibition;
To coordinate with exhibition venue/ contractors/ external partners to ensure the successful running of the exhibition;
To prepare exhibition evaluation reports to achieve continuous improvement;
To assist in marketing plan / materials, coordinating with 3rd parties to ensure effective promotion for the exhibition;
To brainstorm content creation with other team members for advertising, PR and social media initiatives.
